Package org.mvplugins.multiverse.core.world.generators

Class GeneratorProvider

java.lang.Object
org.mvplugins.multiverse.core.world.generators.GeneratorProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.bukkit.event.Listener
@Service public final class GeneratorProvider extends Object implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
Parse the default world generators from the bukkit config and load any generator plugins. Helps in suggesting and validating generator strings.
